Mary BOT 04-Jul-20 06:00 PM
Syntax: $like <character> This will add the character to your list of liked characters. - $likepos <position> <character>: insert a character at a specific position (and move down others) Can also work like $sortmarrypos - $likeremove <character>: remove a character. - $likeclear: clear your list after confirmation. - $likelist: get your list (options listed in $help under the category options/filters list) - $likedm to make your lists private. - $ly to like without confirm above 10 characters in your likelist. For multiple characters, separate them with a $ You can also use series list: add a for Animanga series or g for Game series ($la, $lg, $lra...) Lists: $llanim, $llgame When your list reaches at least 10 characters, you unlock the $daily command to stack a free rolls reset (usable every 20 hours) Note: your list will be part of the global like calculation only if you already voted on https://top.gg/bot/432610292342587392/vote
